3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a new method to improve the energy efficiency of deep neural networks, which is a key aspect of AI research. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper focuses on optimizing the quantization of neural network weights and activations, which is a subfield of neural computing. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a new method for dividing the quantization range into non-overlapping regions, which involves designing an algorithm for finding optimal breakpoints.
